  "concentration": true,
  "description": "You magically mark one creature you can see within range as your quarry. Until the spell ends, you deal an extra [[/damage]] damage to the target whenever you hit it with an attack roll. You also have Advantage on any [[/check ability=wis skill=prc]] or [[/check ability=wis skill=sur]] check you make to find it.\n\nIf the target drops to 0 Hit Points before this spell ends, you can take a Bonus Action to move the mark to a new creature you can see within range.\n\nUsing a Higher-Level Spell Slot.\u00a0Your Concentration can last longer with a spell slot of level 3\u20134 (up to 8 hours) or 5+ (up to 24 hours).",
